WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.210 --> 00:00:04.040
- LearnStorm is an exciting way

00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:05.960
to jump-start your school year.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.170
It's designed to motivate your students

00:00:08.170 --> 00:00:10.830
and to help build their growth mindset.

00:00:10.830 --> 00:00:12.560
- Your intelligence can grow

00:00:12.560 --> 00:00:14.110
just like your muscles can grow.

00:00:14.110 --> 00:00:16.800
- I did over 300 lessons in one week.

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:18.470
I felt proud of myself.

00:00:18.470 --> 00:00:20.960
- It helps the students tremendously.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.630
Their confidence is higher

00:00:22.630 --> 00:00:25.960
and they know that they can
keep going and keep growing

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:28.133
and nothing will stand in their way.

